Becasue [`f(x)`] has no holes, Graph 3 is not a suitable image for the graph of [`f(x)`]. 

However, [`f(x)`] has a horizontal asymptote at [`y = \displaystyle{\frac{3}{1}} = 3`] is . So the graph of [`f(x)`] should reflect:
* Horizontal asymptote [`y=3`]
* Vertical asymptote [`x=-1`]
* No holes

This leaves us with Graph 1 as the best option for the graph of [`f(x)`].

